<p class="ql-align-justify">22岁的硕士郭柏妍表演女团舞，而她是今年的港姐季军：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200830/f32397bf780142e887523987eefb0c4a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
